{"tid":131562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元州邨公園 女子尼龍繩上吊亡","createTime":"2017-02-23T06:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T07:04:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd507280c5e1d4762e6844e25d6d4f90da21e757","tid":131562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170223/19937807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170223%2F19937807&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9zA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=027414de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170223%2F19937807&h=f8de5dd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170223/19937807</a><br />\n<br />\n元州邨公園<br />\n女子尼龍繩上吊亡<br />\n<br />\n6,418<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】長沙灣元州邨對開公園，一名老婦在尼龍繩上吊被途人發現，消防員到場解下老婦再其醫院搶救，最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n一名姓梁85歲老婦，在長沙灣元州邨對開公園涼亭用尼龍繩上吊，昨日早上6時許有途人經過時發現隨即報警。消防員到場將昏迷老婦解下，送明愛醫院搶救最終不治。警方現場撿獲一把雨傘、一張摺凳及一袋物品，現正調查其尋死原因。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n電廠工遭活埋　妻認屍哭暈<br />\n下一則<br />\n千人排隊觀音借庫　善信年年借1.2億"},{"pid":"c8d366dc9251a1a14d5f7e130cb95b1460aafe5e","tid":131562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170223/org/1487794555_e843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170223%2Forg%2F1487794555_e843.jpg&h=737d25b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f56aea6f50601d07b79ea39d76d248e490e7ab3","tid":131562,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac23862a6031d33e24516d60700d435a09993f4d","tid":131562,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:04:3